{"word":"ὑποκάθημαι","slug":"ὑποκάθημαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποκάθημαι</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>-κάτημαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be seated in</i> a place, <i>station oneself</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sit</i> or <i>lie in ambush</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to lie in wait for</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}